ActNunavut Act
SubjectRelinquishment by the Commissioner of Nunavut (approximately .735 hectares)
PrecisOrder a) approving the relinquishment by the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, of the administration and control of approximately .735 hectares of land located in Iqaluit, Nunavut; and b) transfering of the administration of the land to the Minister of Public Safety for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police.
